<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们都认不出对方了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊？”潘瑟一边问一边去碰一个小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他有着黑色的卷发和清澈的蓝眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟？”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摸到的是她挽成一个扣的金色长卷发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟的头发之前通常是棕色直发，发型也非常简单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁有镜子？”简问。“我看上去怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简也漂亮极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的短发是红色的，微微卷着坠在脸旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的皮肤像玫瑰一样娇嫩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还有了一双像绿宝石一样的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道为什么每个人都想变漂亮。”鲍比抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是你的主意，对不对，潘瑟？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我许了愿，”潘瑟承认了，“但我很高兴可以美丽一次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好，很漂亮，你们都是。”休伊打断了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你们走吧。记得，你们的愿望日落时就会消失。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊缩回了他的壳里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊小心地将他送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们走回了镇上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多人开始盯着他们看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定很美，因为每个人都在看我。”潘瑟想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那一刻，她认出了玛莎阿姨的邻居。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！那是贝克尔先生。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝克尔先生在遛他的狗，西尔弗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，贝克尔先生！你好，西尔弗！”潘瑟开心地叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟很喜欢小动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们来玛莎阿姨家后很快就认识了贝克尔先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但现在贝克尔先生和西尔弗看上去都不认识她了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汪！汪！”西尔弗愤怒地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，西尔弗？是我啊，潘瑟！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟弯下腰去轻拍狗狗的脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心点，小姑娘！”贝克尔先生警告说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不然我的狗可能会咬你的手的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看着他的邻居。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝克尔先生，我是鲍比巴斯。”他说，“我们住在隔壁的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝克尔先生怀疑地看看每个孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道你们这些孩子是谁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坚持说，“但我绝对从来没见过你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，但是……”潘瑟走上前想要解释。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，西尔弗冲了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟快步退后，但西尔弗把贝克尔先生手里牵着的皮绳拽掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都被吓了一跳，转身就跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条狗兴奋地边追边叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑！”赛伊大叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们朝着他们阿姨的房子跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望玛莎阿姨在家！”潘瑟大口喘着气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幸运的是，前门是开着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快！”赛伊朝他的兄弟姐妹们大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他等所有人跑进门之后大力关上了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时候西尔弗刚好跑到了门前的台阶那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都瘫在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就差一点点了。”鲍比大声地叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“西尔弗为什么要追我？它喜欢我的！”潘瑟伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她美丽的双眼里满是泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你看上去不一样了。”赛伊解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这并不能让潘瑟感觉好一点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在整个家里找玛莎阿姨和兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她不在家。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都跟着他进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许她去买东西了？”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我饿了。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要吃点东西。”他打开了冰箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去冲个澡。”赛伊说着就上了楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来吧，潘瑟！”简握着她的手，“我们去换身衣服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟仔细地打量着她的兄弟们还有妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的声音听上去还是一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但当潘瑟看着他们的脸时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那感觉就好像她和一群陌生人待在房子里一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>